# RQ-53-10-01-180: Digital Twin Structural Health

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall be equipped with CAOS sensors for real-time structural health monitoring and Digital Twin integration.

## Rationale
Enable predictive maintenance and automated damage assessment.

## Acceptance Criteria
- 12 strain gauges at critical locations
- 3-axis accelerometers for impact detection
- Data transmission to CAOS at 100 Hz
- Integration with Digital Twin framework

## Compliance Status
Sensor layout defined, installation procedure in work
